snippet: The Asian soccer powers Japan, South Korea and Australia took steps toward automatic qualification for the 2014 World Cup.
abstract: Japan plays to a 1-1 draw with Australia and South Korea defeats Lebanon, 3-0, taking steps toward automatic qualification for the 2014 World Cup.
lead_paragraph: The Asian soccer powers Japan, South Korea and Australia took steps toward automatic qualification for the 2014 World Cup.

headline.seo: Japan Ties Australia in World Cup Qualifier
